<p><span class="logical-link-wrap"><a href="/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file</a><span class="logical-link-internal logical-link-internal-false"><span class="logical-link-title logical-link-link-true"><a href="/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">Dr. Cimmerian的人事档案</a></span><span class="logical-link-custom logical-link-link-true"><a href="/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">▸ 该作者的更多作品 ◂</a></span></span><span class="logical-link-original logical-link-original-false"><span class="logical-link-appended">（<a href="http://scpwiki.com/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">原文链接</a>）</span><span class="logical-link-title logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://scpwiki.com/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file</a></span><span class="logical-link-custom logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://scpwiki.com/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">▸ 该作者的更多作品 ◂</a></span></span><span class="logical-link-mark-common logical-link-mark-mark-false" style="color: #009966"><sup><span class="fa fa-link"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></sup></span><span class="logical-link-mark-newpage logical-link-mark-mark-false" style="color: #F00"><sup><span class="fa fa-link"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></sup></span></span></p>
